_:fd1828836a70af59424a3757eb08eff7 a <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E52_Time-span> ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P78_is_identified_by> " He was a monk of the 14th-15th century, considered to be by several hagiographic sources to have been the founder of the monastic community at \n                  ʿAddǝqe of Eritrea. Though the date and place of birth is unknown clearly, \n                  he entered the monastery of Dabra Māryām\n                  of Qʷaḥayn, which was founded by \n                \n                   \n                     ʾabbā \n                     ʾAbsādi of Dabra Māryām in 1390/91. \n                  He spent then the whole life in this monastery." .
